<h2><hr/><p align="center"> Notepad</p><hr/>
</h2><img src="https://www.w3schools.com/html/img_notepad.png" width="482" height="249">
<p> If you can't download NetBeans IDE you can use your notepad or a simple txt editor, then you need to write the program and save it with the file extension "<strong>.html</strong>"
 then click on the icon that appear on the desktop and see your results. Enjoy :).
</p>
<p> If you need to edit the file again: right click on the icon and than change the file extension again in "<strong>.txt</strong>".
</p>
